title: Final Preseason Week 1 Takeaway
itunes:title: Final Preseason Week 1 Takeaway
description:
A room filled with heroes – Dan Hanzus, Chris Wesseling, Marc Sessler & Gregg Rosenthal – recap all the latest news from around the NFL including Roberto Aguayo’s cut from Tampa Bay and Andrew Luck’s vague expected start. The heroes give their final recap of the remaining eight games concluding the first week of preseason.
